        "question_text": "A 5 kg block is placed on a horizontal surface with μ=0.2. A 30 N force is applied (g=10 m/s²). What is the acceleration?",
        "options": { "A": "6 m/s²", "B": "4 m/s²", "C": "2 m/s²", "D": "5 m/s²" },
